data.description: Updated 2 bedroom home in beautiful Ormond Beach.  Two bedroom one bath home is within walking distance from the no-drive beach. This home features an updated kitchen with granite countertops, wood cabinets with plenty of storage, tile throughout, fresh paint, new insulation, new roof, plantation shutters, paver driveway, inside laundry and a beautiful tropical landscaped yard. No HOA fees! Washer and dryer are included. This move in ready home won't last long. Just bring your toothbrush and start enjoying your new beachside retreat.
